commit e5b9bb7facfe14af8fb0eecd415690b8295a2aca
Author: Vendula Poncova <vponcova@redhat.com>
Date:   Wed Feb 17 12:26:19 2021 +0100

    Don't translate the prompt keys
    
    Translated prompt keys are not supported by the simpleline library,
    so don't mark them for translation.
    
    Related: rhbz#1892830

