commit 43bca7e2c6ce88d4dfafccbbbaa90053eae39a51
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Wed Feb 17 17:34:16 2021 +0100

    Use Fedora container registry instead of Dockerhub
    
    First, they are more up to date so we will avoid issue with bad GPG keys we have
    now.
    Second, there is no limit for downloads.

