commit 45a0adf3b55136b6e076e38f518ccf57d353cd42
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Wed Aug 5 12:37:38 2020 +0200

    Use relative imports in tests
    
    This will improve usage of tests out of the source tree testing. Reason is that
    the top level git has simpleline folder and current solution was `from test
    import ...` which means that PYTHONPATH is set to the root of the git.

