commit 9b771ef2c2e33cb2d246a1146a8edf39de0c3ee1
Merge: 3e0e7db 724fa8c
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 18 13:58:10 2020 +0200

    Merge pull request #71 from jkonecny12/master-support-change-setup-args
    
    Add possibility to change setup.py arguments

commit 724fa8c5ba6475f985cfe16bad9640a4a0f090d8
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Wed Jun 17 09:48:03 2020 +0200

    Add possibility to change setup.py arguments
    
    By default we want to create an archive with bdist_wheel which will also
    create metadata for PYPI distribution. However, dbist_wheel have another
    dependency package which may not be by default installed and it is not
    required for spec file creation at all.
    
    Add setup.py arguments as Makefile variable.

