commit 6372acb5a34d682f5e4039396d2206c088e75adc
Merge: 9805f3d 84fcb16
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Mon May 28 11:27:13 2018 +0200

    Merge pull request #55 from jkonecny12/master-more-robust-makefile
    
