commit bf0d458153a526297cd1b8df064a28d54b963d90
Author: Jiri Konecny <jkonecny@redhat.com>
Date:   Thu May 17 11:52:35 2018 +0200

    Add missing newline characters at the end
    
    When widget contained \n character at the end of the text this character
    was skipped. Fix this behavior by extending the buffer at the end if
    required.
    
    Also fix tests.

